org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.impl

Class AbstractGroupingByEntityDialect

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.BaseGridDialect
      • org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.impl.AbstractGroupingByEntityDialect
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, GroupingByEntityDialect, GridDialect, Service
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractRedisDialect, CouchDBDialect

    public abstract class AbstractGroupingByEntityDialect
extends BaseGridDialect
implements GroupingByEntityDialect
    Base class of all GridDialects implementing the grouping of operations per entity.

    The idea is to group all the insert/update operations regarding the same entity in one datastore operation.

    Author:
    Guillaume Smet
